  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 110 \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Petrol price to be reduced by Rs 110 - United Union of Trade Unions report",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The organizer of the United Union of Trade Unions Ananda Balitha said that the price of fuel in Sri Lanka should be reduced compared to the price of fuel in the world market.",
        "\"As fuel prices are falling rapidly in the world market, fuel prices should be significantly reduced as per the price formula proposed by the government.",
        "16 days ago, the price of a barrel of oil in the world market was seen at 145 dollars. However, currently the price of a barrel of oil in the world market has decreased to 104 dollars. Therefore, its benefits should be given to the people.",
        "After collecting all the taxes, the price of 92 octane petrol can be reduced by Rs 110 from the existing price, 95 octane petrol by Rs 120 and a liter of super diesel by Rs 120,\u201d he said.",
        "He further mentioned that these price reductions will not cause any loss to Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation."
      ],
